## Writing from anywhere ##
I want to be able to write my ideas from anywhere, even when offline
So that I don't forget any of them because of technical reasons.

### Propagating modifications ###
Given a modification I made on my netbook
When I publish it
Then I can access it from my desktop computer

## Refactoring writings ##
I want to be able to rework easily my writings
So that I can organize them more clearly.
